# Capstone Project - Web Application Pentesting (DVWA)

## Objective
To identify vulnerabilities in a web application using DVWA.

## Tools Used
- Kali Linux
- DVWA
- Nmap
- Hydra

## Attacks Performed
- SQL Injection
- Brute Force Attack (Hydra)
- Cross Site Scripting (XSS)

## Results
Successfully identified vulnerabilities and demonstrated attacks.

